@@TJvRle
Description:
This component is an implementation of an RLE algorithm. This RLE implementation is compatible with the one used in the PCX file format.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvRle.Compress@TStream
Description:
Use this method to compress a stream using the RLE compression algorithm

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvRle.Decompress@TStream
Description:
Use this method to decompress a stream using the RLE compression algorithm

